men-journalists-in-crime-fiction/">Fiona Barton on Women Journalists in Crime Fiction</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">August 27, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/fionabarton/">Fiona Barton</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/forgiveness-redemption-crime-fiction/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/08/forgiveness-feat-1-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/forgiveness-redemption-crime-fiction/">Forgive, but Don't Forget: On Redemption in Crime Fiction</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">August 27, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/adammitzner/">Adam Mitzner</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/natural-born-killers-30-years/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2024/08/natural-born-killers-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/natural-born-killers-30-years/">Love Kills the Demon: 30 Years of Natural Born Killers</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">August 26, 2024</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/martynconterio/">Martyn Conterio</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
